ValueSetStatus

The lifecycle status of a Value Set

This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/valueset-status

CodeDisplayDefinition
draftThis valueset is still under development.
activeThis valueset is ready for normal use.
retiredThis valueset has been withdrawn or superceded and should no longer be used.
